  m_text: "How Difficulty Works\r\n\r\nAdaptive\r\nLumi watches how the child performs
    and adjusts automatically.\r\nGood rounds make it harder. Tough rounds make it
    easier.\r\nUse this to let the child grow at their own pace.\r\n\r\nFixed\r\nEvery
    level stays exactly the same every session.\r\nUse this for consistent, repeatable
    therapy sessions.\r\n\r\n  Level 1 \u2014 1 fruit  \xB7  2\xD72 grid  \xB7  1s
    delay\r\n  Level 2 \u2014 2 fruits \xB7  3\xD73 grid  \xB7  1.5s delay\r\n  Level
    3 \u2014 3 fruits \xB7  4\xD74 grid  \xB7  2s delay\r\n  Level 4 \u2014 3 fruits
    \xB7  4\xD74 grid  \xB7  2.5s delay"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 65a72620f8226464a83d3225274b5edd, type: 2}
